Detailed Description

POD structure containing all problems data.

This gathers together several information from which functions parameters are set.

cnoid::BodyMotionPtr roboptim::retargeting::JointFunctionData::jointsTrajectory

Joints Trajectory as loaded by Choreonoid.

This file both contains the joints parameters at each frame as well as the base position at each frame.

This trajectory contains the full motion.
